strings: <voice_0x01000B9A><se_low>*: ...are...? How troublesome is being in the air!
<voice_0x01000B9B><se_low>*: Who are you, do you want to talk to me?
<voice_0x01000B9C><se_def>*: That's it! ,: Bass!
<voice_0x01000B9D><se_def>*: This spell is for Father François's life!
<voice_0x01000B9E><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: To make me feel better...!? Are you here?
<voice_0x01000B9F><se_def>Awesome!: Father Francisco Marcelo Captain as usual!
<voice_0x01000BA0><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: Oh, Marcela! Please explain to him what is going on.
<voice_0x01000BA1><se_def>Awesome!: There was a break, many officers were seriously injured.
<voice_0x01000BA2><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: What is it?
<voice_0x01000BA3><se_def>Awesome!: I think you're in danger, so I'll be there soon...
<voice_0x01000BA4><se_def>Awesome!: Of course, we still have to catch the bad guys. In the evening we went to the temple.
<voice_0x01000BA5><se_def>Awesome!: It seems like it's just in time. I'm glad everything went well.
<voice_0x01000BA6><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: ... pregnant! These people are not criminals.
<voice_0x01000BA7><se_def>Awesome!: Watch out dad, you're caught!
<voice_0x01000BA8><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: Look into their eyes, look into their pure hearts, these people have done nothing wrong.
<voice_0x01000BA9><se_def>Awesome!: In any case...!
<voice_0x01000BAA><se_def>Awesome!: It says on the right! But we need to know what was done at his house late at night.
<voice_0x01000BAB><se_def>Awesome!: At least it's being confirmed. I want you
<voice_0x01000BAC><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: Hi Marcelo, you must be very worried! Please release it if you like!
<voice_0x01000BAD><se_def>Awesome!: thank you dad
<voice_0x01000BAE><se_def>Awesome!: ......let's go together?
